Package GUI.panels

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDungeonPanel
    The interface for all panels in the gui.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BattlePanel
    The panel that handles all the battles between a player and another actor.
    EndGamePanel
    The panel that shows end game results.
    MainMenuPanel
    The panel that holds the startgame button.
    MainPanel
    Panel for the player, it shows player status and items, and the possible locations to move into.
    MoveResultPanel
    Is created when the actor moves.
    PlayerNamePanel
    The panel which asks the names of the players.
    SetPlayerCountPanel
    The panel that allows the player to set player count for the game.
    SettingsPanel  
    TurnPanel
    Appears when the turn is changed.
